beer.beer_description: This malty gem combines the best of the Celtic region with its beautiful malts and hops. We have teamed it up with an old English yeast to throw flavours of raisin, roast and hints of nutmeg creating a cracking ale with the deep red hue that charred malt brings to beer. Delivered by hand pump this ale is low in carbonation and smooth.

items.badge_description: Celebrate women and non-binary individuals in craft beer! Every year the Pink Boots Society (PBS) hosts Collaboration Brew Day where teams come together to brew a collab beer that supports the PBS mission to support, inspire, and encourage the professional development of women and non-binary people in the industry.
